{"tid":405404,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【向股東伸手】先施擬「5供3」供股 最多籌逾9,800萬作還債","createTime":"2017-09-18T23:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T23:37:01.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"213b248049b598f6e9444f390afbfe98460d2467","tid":405404,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T23:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170918/large/1505747811_abbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170918%2Flarge%2F1505747811_abbc.jpg&h=e45be466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先施(244)宣佈以「每5股供3股」比例供股，供股價為每股0.27元，較今日收市價元折讓約28%，集資額介乎9,300至9,870萬元，所得款項淨額中不少於8,500及不超過9,000萬元，將用作償還貸款，餘下用作百貨業務的一般營運資金。大股東已承諾供股，由於擬新增股份數目高於現行股本50%，供股方案須召開股東會，待獨立股東批准通過，方能作實。<br />\n<br />\n是次供股的包銷商為Win Dynamic，由先施股東之一的馬景煊及非執董陳文衛，各自持有75%及25%股權，供股股份將由包銷商按包銷協議所載條款及條件，悉數包銷。<br />\n<br />\n先施目前已發行股數為3.446億股，當中與包銷商一致行動人士合共持有45.36%。假設合資格股東（包銷商除外）並無接納供股，緊隨供股完成後，與包銷商一致行動人士的股權將升至66.46%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57227333&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57227333%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170918&d=DCax3CkWc1bxFmIsD2oIJ10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6e90cbd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57227333%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170918&h=4e7ef882\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57227333&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170918</a>"}]}